Titolo: Moss (video game)

Anno: 2018

Descrizione: Moss is a virtual reality adventure game developed and published by American video game development studio Polyarc. The game is presented from a blend of first-person and third-person perspectives, with a primary focus on solving puzzles. Moss was released for the PlayStation 4 in February 2018. In June, a PC version featuring high-resolution graphics was released.A sequel, Moss: Book 2, was announced by Polyarc during Sony's State of Play in 2021.

Genere: Adventure 

Valutazione: N/A
